### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
### Customers
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### GET Customer by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/customers/1

### POST Create Customer
POST http://localhost:5000/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Helene",
    "lastName": "Fischer",
    "email": "helene.fischer@gmx.at",
    "password": "SecurePassword123!",
    "phone": "1234567",
    "address": {
        "street": "Spengergasse 20",
        "zip": "1050",
        "city": "Wien",
        "country": "AT"
    }
}

### POST Create Customer (duplicate email -> 409 Conflict)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Other",
    "lastName": "Person",
    "email": "max.mustermann@spengergasse.at",
    "password": "SecurePassword123!",
    "address": {
        "street": "Teststr. 1",
        "zip": "1010",
        "city": "Wien",
        "country": "AT"
    }
}

### PUT Update Customer (full update)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Updated",
    "lastName": "Name",
    "phone": "9999999",
    "address": {
        "street": "Neue Str. 5",
        "zip": "1020",
        "city": "Wien",
        "country": "AT"
    }
}

### PATCH Change Customer Name (partial update)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "NewFirst",
    "lastName": "NewLast"
}

### DELETE Customer
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/customers/1

### GET Customer (not found -> 404)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/customers/999